-- (optional) prepare a response.
-- --
-- Conventions:
-- S = create (re)start state
-- P = create stop state
-- E4W = master writes 0x4E
-- R   = master reads and ACKs
-- N   = master reads and NACKs
-- --
-- s5Cw80ws5Dwrnp - reads application code and version (0x31 0x01)
-- s5Cw90w00wp    - LED off
-- s5Cw90wFFwp    - LED on 
